## Pyrenean region hosts 4 karst springs from 2 countries.

Spanish data is provided by Jorge Jodar (j.jodar@igme.es),
French data are provided by 

Jean-Baptiste Charlier (j.charlier@brgm.fr) and 
Sandra Beranger (s.beranger@brgm.fr).

Original data source is Eaufrance hydroportail platform "https://www.hydro.eaufrance.fr/".

For further information, please see the Metadata table.
